=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實真係好嬲好嬲好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實因咩事鬧交?</blockquote><br />\n啲小事依家真係諗唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚係本身約左出去 <br />\n點知佢甩我底同朋友打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最憎男朋友放飛機 即刻屌撚到佢反皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31f6ef8fef057394292c44baef79747854a1493","tid":100851,"uid":26241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最耐個次兩星期☹️其實已經係分手 唔係冷戰咁簡單<br />\n真係冷靜通常2日 好難受</blockquote><br />\n兩星期真係好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種好想揾佢又好嬲既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔會 次次都係我搵佢先<br />\n兩星期個次點解咁長 因為我無搵<br />\n心淡到 日日搵fd 陪 日日都去fd 屋企訓 <br />\n以自放低左 點知佢搵返我 先好返<br />\n如果唔係我諗已經分左手"},{"pid":"ff59acae798f8201929a15f15a09341d538e4081","tid":100851,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"1日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7332332f81928f0719364e81365dd6057ceca8ef","tid":100851,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:15:15.000Z","msg":"個半月"},{"pid":"74120545a1d0d1eaca699a6a57479897b7c0fbd2","tid":100851,"uid":65005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"一世，然後我就